Core Theme for [`@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-{{kebabCase name}}`](https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-themes/tree/master/themes/gatsby-theme-{{kebabCase name}}). This theme implements the TODO node interfaces and exports templates (+ queries) which you can shadow.

Also, be sure to checkout other [Free & Open Source Gatsby Themes](https://themes.lekoarts.de)

## Installation

```sh
npm install @lekoarts/gatsby-theme-{{kebabCase name}}-core
```

## Usage

### Theme options

| Key              | Default Value | Description                                                                                                                           |
| ---------------- | ------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `option` | `{}`          | text |

### Shadowing

Please read the guide [Shadowing in Gatsby Themes](https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/themes/shadowing/) to understand how to customize this theme! You can also have a look at [`@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-{{kebabCase name}}`](https://github.com/LekoArts/gatsby-themes/tree/master/themes/gatsby-theme-{{kebabCase name}}) to see it in action. Generally speaking you will want to place your files into `src/@lekoarts/gatsby-theme-{{kebabCase name}}-core/` to shadow/override files.

